title: CD Chingale
text:
The Clube dos Desportos de Chingale is a <a href="Mozambique">Mozambican</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Tete">Tete</a>. They play in the top division in Mozambican football, <a href="Mo%C3%A7ambola">Moçambola</a>. Their home stadium is <a href="Est%C3%A1dio%20do%20Chingale">Estádio do Chingale</a>.
The club was originally founded as Futebol Clube de Tete in the 1950s, and was re-named Sporting Clube do Tete in 1964. In 1981, the club was re-named Clube dos Desportos de Chingale.
